(1039, 1, '2020-10-01 13:07:45', '2020-10-01 11:07:45', '<img width=\"680\" height=\"439\" src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/dozer1.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/dozer1.png 680w, http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/dozer1-300x194.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\">\n<h4>7 Years of field experience</h4>\n<h2>We Are The</h2>\n<h2><strong>NEXT Generation Builders</strong></h2>\nJust call us. Constructionwise there\'s nothing that we haven\'t done yet. We are the magicians in the world of Construction.\n\n<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\nGet a Quote\n</a>\n<h3>\n					Construction</h3>\nConstruction is our main work. We can construct anything imaginable except for the ladder to heaven. Need help? We are just a call away.\n<h3>\n					Design</h3>\nDesign is our main work. We can design anything imaginable except for the ladder to heaven.​ Need help? We are just a call away.\n<h3>\n					Repair</h3>\nRepair is our main work. We can repair anything imaginable except for the ladder to heaven.​ Need help? We are just a call away.\n<h3>\n					Renovation</h3>\nDesign is our main work. We can design anything imaginable except for the ladder to heaven.​ Need help? We are just a call away.\n<h3>\n					Material Supply</h3>\nConstruction is our main work. We can construct anything imaginable except for the ladder to heaven. Need help? We are just a call away.\n<h3>\n					Interior Design</h3>\nRepair is our main work. We can repair anything imaginable except for the ladder to heaven.​ Need help? We are just a call away.\n<h3>Our projects</h3>\nClick on the images below to learn more about the individual projects.\n<img width=\"377\" height=\"431\" src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/project-tower.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/project-tower.png 377w, http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/project-tower-262x300.png 262w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 377px) 100vw, 377px\">\n<h4>Pencil Tower</h4>\n<img width=\"377\" height=\"431\" src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/midtown-church.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/midtown-church.png 377w, http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/midtown-church-262x300.png 262w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 377px) 100vw, 377px\">\n<h4>Midtown Church</h4>\n<img width=\"377\" height=\"431\" src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/project-hotel.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/project-hotel.png 377w, http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/project-hotel-262x300.png 262w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 377px) 100vw, 377px\">\n<h4>Project 5 Star</h4>\n<img width=\"580\" height=\"332\" src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/bridge-580-by-332.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/bridge-580-by-332.png 580w, http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/bridge-580-by-332-300x172.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\">\n<h4>Twisting Bridge</h4>\n<img width=\"580\" height=\"331\" src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/colony-580-by-332.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/colony-580-by-332.png 580w, http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/colony-580-by-332-300x171.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\">\n<h4>Happy colony</h4>\n<h3>Professionals Behind</h3>\nKnow our team, engineers and architects behind our construction team. We are people that find passion in what we do.\n\n<img width=\"291\" height=\"291\" src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/25388788904_72d2f5ec6f_z.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/25388788904_72d2f5ec6f_z.jpg 291w, http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/25388788904_72d2f5ec6f_z-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 291px) 100vw, 291px\">\n<h4>Ivana Rastokiva</h4>\nArchitect\n\nKnow our team, engineers, architects behind our construction team. We are people that find passion in what we do.\n\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\nFacebook\n</a>\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\nTwitter\n</a>\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\nGoogle-plus\n</a>\n<img width=\"268\" height=\"275\" src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/team_4.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n<h4>Mathew Hipler</h4>\nStructural Engineer\n\nKnow our team, engineers, architects behind our construction team. We are people that find passion in what we do.\n\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\nFacebook\n</a>\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\nTwitter\n</a>\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\nGoogle-plus\n</a>\n<img width=\"269\" height=\"275\" src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/team_2.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n<h4>Mike Thierry</h4>\nField Engineer\n\nKnow our team, engineers, architects behind our construction team. We are people that find passion in what we do.\n\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\nFacebook\n</a>\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\nTwitter\n</a>\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\nGoogle-plus\n</a>\n<h3>What our clients say</h3>\nDon\'t take our word, hear it from our clients. Client happiness is our utmost priority.\n\n\"I really like their work, I guess now they have got a new lifetime customer. From now on, every construction project that I do will only be via their construction company.\"\n<img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/team_3-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\">\nIvanika Christopher\nManager, R &amp; B Group\n\"I really like their work, I guess now they have got a new lifetime customer. From now on, every construction project that I do will only be via their construction company.\"\n<img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/team_3-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\">\nIvanika Christopher\nManager, R &amp; B Group\n<h3>Our pricing</h3>\nLearn about our pricing. While there are many factors that affect pricing. Following pricing is for standard situation.\n<h4>Basic</h4>\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n										Small to Mid House</li>\n 	<li>\n										Upto 10 Interior Objects</li>\n 	<li>\n										1 Year Repair Coverage</li>\n 	<li>\n										Upto 4000 sq. feet</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>$(19-39)</h4>\n<h5>per sq. feet</h5>\n<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\nGet a Quote\n</a>\n<h4>Standard</h4>\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n										Mid House to Complex</li>\n 	<li>\n										Upto 25 Interior Objects</li>\n 	<li>\n										2 Year Repair Coverage</li>\n 	<li>\n										Upto 10,000 sq. feet</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>$(39-59)</h4>\n<h5>per sq. feet</h5>\n<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\nGet a Quote\n</a>\n<h4>Corporate</h4>\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n										Huge Structures</li>\n 	<li>\n										Upto 100 Interior Objects</li>\n 	<li>\n										5 Year Repair Coverage</li>\n 	<li>\n										Above 10,000 sq. feet</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>$(59-99)</h4>\n<h5>per sq. feet</h5>\n<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\nGet a Quote\n</a>\n<h3>Our happy Clients</h3>\n<figure><img src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/logo_1-1-150x128.png\" alt=\"logo_1-1.png\"></figure>\n<figure><img src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/logo_2-1-150x150.png\" alt=\"logo_2-1.png\"></figure>\n<figure><img src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/logo_3-1-150x150.png\" alt=\"logo_3-1.png\"></figure>\n<figure><img src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/logo_4-1-150x150.png\" alt=\"logo_4-1.png\"></figure>\n<figure><img src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/logo_5-1-150x150.png\" alt=\"logo_5-1.png\"></figure>\n<figure><img src=\"http://somecotrad.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/logo_6-1-143x150.png\" alt=\"logo_6-1.png\"></figure>\n<figu